Package main.java.elsim.models

Class Car

java.lang.Object
main.java.elsim.models.Car
public class Car
extends java.lang.Object
Contains all information needed to handle the elevator car for passenger transportation. All information needed to create an elevator car are supplied by the ConfigManager. Main functionality includes the managing of Passenger (adding, removing).
Author:
fwagner
See Also:
ConfigManager, Passenger
